query:
DELETE FROM smtp_credentials c 
                   USING streams s 
                       JOIN projects p ON s.project_id = p.id 
                   WHERE c.stream_id = s.id 
                     AND p.organization_id = $1
                     AND p.id = $2
                     AND s.id = $3 
                     AND c.id = $4
            RETURNING c.id
